(To insert unicode dash type: Ctrl+Shift+u+2014: —)

Ctrl+;          — Semicolon at the end of the line
Ctrl+Shift+;    — Semicolon at the end of the line + goto new line

Alt+Shift+.     — Select text block
Alt+Shift+,     — De-select text block

Ctrl+u+u        — Change selected text to uppercase
Ctrl+u+l        — Change selected text to lowercase
Ctrl+u+l        — Switch case

Ctrl+Shift+↑    — Duplicate line UP
Ctrl+Shift+↓    — Duplicate line DOWN

Ctrl+Space      — Autocomplete
Ctrl+p          — Arguments
Ctrl+Shift+Space — Documentation

Ctrl+g          — GOTO line number
Ctrl+e          — Delete current line or selected block 
Ctrl+e          — GOTO Last edit

Ctrl+Shift+v    — Formatted code insertion 
Alt+Shift+j     — Select identifier 

Shift+Enter     — Same as press End and then Enter

Ctrl+0          — Code editor 
Ctrl+1          — Projects
Ctrl+7          — Navigator


Alt+Shift+o     — Find file by name
Ctrl+o          — Find file by class 

Alt+Ins         — Code generation

